text: Elias Edström (born April 19, 1995) is a Swedish professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing with Tegs SK of the Hockeyettan (Div.1). Edström made his Swedish Hockey League debut playing with Skellefteå AIK during the 2014–15 SHL season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:AIK IF players Category:Asplöven HC players Category:Kristianstads IK players Category:Piteå HC players Category:Skellefteå AIK players Category:Swedish ice hockey forwards Category:IF Troja/Ljungby players
